</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#ffffff><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=demised>Demised</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Journeyman</span><br>  Posts: 15<br> <font color=#000000>(6/22/03 12:13 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=263.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.darkhosts.com/demised/trees5.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Specific Feedback: Flank/DS/DT Changes</span><hr size=1> I agree with everything mentioned above, the changes were for the better in my mind and very glad they actually happened...<br>
<br>
But call me weird, I seem to hit more often with Flank than Shadow's Rain... I can't count how many times I'll be in an RvR situation, nail Flank but whiff on SR, it happens way more often than missing Flank itself...<br>
<br>
But maybe I'm just cursed with horrible chain luck <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.darkhosts.com/demised/chainwall.gif"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#c0c0c0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=nalfen>Nalfen</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://mapage.noos.fr/philemon.levesque/nalfen.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Initiate</span><br>  Posts: 5<br> <font color=#000000>(6/22/03 4:42 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=263.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Specific Feedback: Flank/DS/DT Changes</span><hr size=1> DS changes are excellent the bleed make for a decent fight starter and compensate the defence penality.<br>
<br>
I have still yet to be impressed by flank/ds. Flank hardly outdamage Amy slash and misses often. Dual shadow as always been a decent style but i usually do not go through the hassle to try to pull it off. In RVR i removed them from my Qbars but still use them in pve.<br>
<br>
Dark tendrills, im biased over this one. I used to rely on it being an evade reactive (i evade quite a bit having high quick and dex) now i just use reflexion as a parry reactive, i don't think i could use another parry reactive. The bleed damage should be a little higher because that style misses often on high AF classes.<br>
<br>
<br>
Other things:<br>
<br>
Misty gloom is still probably one of the worst style in the game. <br>
<br>
We still have 2 moves off the same style that are basically the same moves. (penumbra and eclipse)<br>
<br>
<br>
Those are a change toward the right direction.<br>
<br>
Keep it up kate<br>
<br>
